3) 6-3 6-2 defeat\", \"from\": 746, \"to\": 770}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A lack of physical durability has been Draper's Achilles heel and he admitted that he was not able to handle the conditions having so far played through a cool European summer.\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 978, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 841, \"end\": 847, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Draper\", \"score\": 0.9975555668927182, \"rank\": 0.002391242161555977, \"text\": \"Draper\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Draper\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Draper\"}, {\"begin\": 850, \"end\": 858, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"score\": 0.9999694732280832, \"rank\": 3.052770378893935e-05, \"text\": \"Achilles\", \"types\": [\"Q4936952\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Achilles_tendon\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A lack\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 808}, {\"ngram\": \"physical durability\", \"from\": 812, \"to\": 831}, {\"ngram\": \"the conditions\", \"from\": 911, \"to\": 925}, {\"ngram\": \"a cool European summer\", \"from\": 955, \"to\": 977}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he also hit out at the provisions for players to rehydrate.\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 1043, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the provisions\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1017}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 1022, \"to\": 1029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In an effort to be more environmentally friendly, tennis players are now supplied with refillable bottles, but Draper found himself unable to keep his water cool, and spending the changes of ends standing up at a water fountain.\", \"from\": 1044, \"to\": 1272, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an effort\", \"from\": 1047, \"to\": 1056}, {\"ngram\": \"tennis players\", \"from\": 1094, \"to\": 1108}, {\"ngram\": \"refillable bottles\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1149}, {\"ngram\": \"Draper\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1161}, {\"ngram\": \"his water\", \"from\": 1191, \"to\": 1200}, {\"ngram\": \"the changes\", \"from\": 1220, \"to\": 1231}, {\"ngram\": \"ends\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1239}, {\"ngram\": \"a water fountain\", \"from\": 1255, \"to\": 1271}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was tough conditions, there is no doubt about it,\\\" said Draper as he dripped with sweat.\", \"from\": 1274, \"to\": 1366, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tough conditions\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1298}, {\"ngram\": \"no doubt\", \"from\": 1309, \"to\": 1317}, {\"ngram\": \"Draper\", \"from\": 1334, \"to\": 1340}, {\"ngram\": \"sweat\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1365}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I need to play more in this sort of heat, and obviously, going to America, I will get more used to that.\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1472, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this sort\", \"from\": 1391, \"to\": 1400}, {\"ngram\": \"heat\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1408}, {\"ngram\": \"America\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1441}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was really hot out there today.\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1507, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We were both trying our best to put out some good tennis.\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1567, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"some good tennis\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1566}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Part of it's physicality but I said to the referee, it's pretty poor that the players have to drink hot water when we are playing in those conditions.\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1718, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Part\", \"from\": 1568, \"to\": 1572}, {\"ngram\": \"physicality\", \"from\": 1581, \"to\": 1592}, {\"ngram\": \"the referee\", \"from\": 1607, \"to\": 1618}, {\"ngram\": \"the players\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1653}, {\"ngram\": \"hot water\", \"from\": 1668, \"to\": 1677}, {\"ngram\": \"those conditions\", \"from\": 1701, \"to\": 1717}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's important we have good fridges to keep our water cool.\", \"from\": 1720, \"to\": 1780, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"good fridges\", \"from\": 1744, \"to\": 1756}, {\"ngram\": \"our water\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1774}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's so tough to recover when you are just not replenishing properly.\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1850, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is no escape from the heat, even at the change of ends.\", \"from\": 1852, \"to\": 1914, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no escape\", \"from\": 1862, \"to\": 1871}, {\"ngram\": \"the heat\", \"from\": 1877, \"to\": 1885}, {\"ngram\": \"the change\", \"from\": 1895, \"to\": 1905}, {\"ngram\": \"ends\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1913}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have not played in much hotter conditions than that.\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 1969, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"much hotter conditions\", \"from\": 1936, \"to\": 1958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your body starts to really fight against you.\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 2015, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your body\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 1979}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We should not have to fill our water up every change of ends, we need to sit down.\", \"from\": 2017, \"to\": 2100, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our water\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2054}, {\"ngram\": \"every change\", \"from\": 2058, \"to\": 2070}, {\"ngram\": \"ends\", \"from\": 2074, \"to\": 2078}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's not good enough.\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2122, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I just think it's pretty poor that they put the players through that on court.\\\"\", \"from\": 2123, \"to\": 2202, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the players\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2178}, {\"ngram\": \"court\", \"from\": 2195, \"to\": 2200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From late in the second set and through the decider, Draper, who had been comfortably the better play during the first half of the match, was barely able to chase down balls.\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2378, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the second set\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2231}, {\"ngram\": \"the decider\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2255}, {\"ngram\": \"Draper\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2263}, {\"ngram\": \"the better play\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2305}, {\"ngram\": \"the first half\", \"from\": 2313, \"to\": 2327}, {\"ngram\": \"the match\", \"from\": 2331, \"to\": 2340}, {\"ngram\": \"balls\", \"from\": 2372, \"to\": 2377}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It might have been a different story had he taken any of nine break points, including six in one game early in the second set, before a double fault handed Fritz the advantage when he broke for 4-2.\", \"from\": 2380, \"to\": 2578, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a different story\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2416}, {\"ngram\": \"nine break points\", \"from\": 2437, \"to\": 2454}, {\"ngram\": \"six in one game\", \"from\": 2466, \"to\": 2481}, {\"ngram\": \"the second set\", \"from\": 2491, \"to\": 2505}, {\"ngram\": \"a double fault\", \"from\": 2514, \"to\": 2528}, {\"ngram\": \"Fritz\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2541}, {\"ngram\": \"the advantage\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The threshold for the extreme weather policy, which permits players a 10-minute break before a deciding set in singles, was reached just after Draper and Fritz walked off court.\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2757, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The threshold\", \"from\": 2580, \"to\": 2593}, {\"ngram\": \"the extreme weather policy\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2624}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 2640, \"to\": 2647}, {\"ngram\": \"a 10-minute break\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2665}, {\"ngram\": \"a deciding\", \"from\": 2673, \"to\": 2683}, {\"ngram\": \"singles\", \"from\": 2691, \"to\": 2698}, {\"ngram\": \"D